147617.name: Coal Production - TWh
147617.description: Includes commercial solid fuels only, i.e. bituminous coal and anthracite (hard coal), and lignite and brown (sub-bituminous) coal, and other commercial solid fuels. Includes coal produced for Coal-to-Liquids and Coal-to-Gas transformations.
147617.datasetName: Statistical Review of World Energy - BP (2021)

source.name: Statistical Review of World Energy - BP (2021)

147633.name: Gas Production - TWh
147633.description: Excludes gas flared or recycled. Includes natural gas produced for Gas-to-Liquids transformation.
147633.datasetName: Statistical Review of World Energy - BP (2021)

source.name: Statistical Review of World Energy - BP (2021)

147658.name: Oil Production - TWh
147658.description: Includes crude oil, shale oil, oil sands, condensates (lease condensate or gas condensates that require further refining) and NGLs (natural gas liquids - ethane, LPG and naphtha separated from the production of natural gas). Excludes liquid fuels from other sources such as biofuels and synthetic derivatives of coal and natural gas. This also excludes liquid fuel adjustment factors such as refinery processing gain. Excludes oil shales/kerogen extracted in solid form.
147658.datasetName: Statistical Review of World Energy - BP (2021)

source.name: Statistical Review of World Energy - BP (2021)
